<span id="freeTextContainer1714168648379518021">I had never read any of these authors before and was quite pleasantly surprised. This is a compilation of absolutely delightful stories set in Regency England at Christmas time. Each one is unique in its own way and very precious. I thoroughly enjoyed this read. Recommended. <br/><br/>*My thanks to the publisher for a preview copy of this book. The opinions stated here are my own. </span>

