<span id="freeTextContainer9214691799472910655">I read this book really only for Christmas At Falstone Castle....because who doesn&apos;t want more stories with the Duke of Kielder! However I was so pleasantly surprised by the other stories that I really ended up loving this whole book. My favorite story is the third one which is written by my new favorite author Esther Hatch. Tis The Season To Be Daring was so fun and the most adorable story! Lord Hawthorne is swoon worthy and I loved getting a better peak at Rose&apos;s family from The Roses Of Felds</span>
