<span id="freeTextContainer11842616991325491953">So much to love about this collection of 4 Christmas themed Historical Romance Novellas. Each story is satisfying, though will leave you wishing it had been a longer fuller story. That’s how great these authors are. <br/><br/>I am left feeling contented, and absolutely of the mind this is the best yet of Covenants Christmas Novellas.</span>

